release_body:
Version 0.3.7 is identical to version 0.3.6, except for the following differences:

 - `pip-review` is now [a separate package with a new maintainer](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pip-review);
 - `pip-dump` has been removed because it was superseded by `pip-compile` from the current [pip-tools package](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pip-tools);
 - the tests have been slightly updated.
